Michael Jackson as a person is likely a fairly quick reads, having composed solo portraits of himself. He's also a prominent figure in popular culture. He has since released 20+ music albums. His passing has been mourned throughout the world: 
- By his fans who called for his possible headstone being removed near his home;
- By the Saints football team who disowned him after the team was accused of sexual misconduct and nepotism;
- By many sports fans who have been offended by his sports use of racial slurs across the video games, chants, songs, videos, and performances.
